answers.body_markdown:
Formaction changes the action of the form, not the function that is used to submit the data with.

You can make an event listener and use preventDefault() to make it not submit the data the usual way. Since it&#39;s not getting sent, you can write your own submission procedure and use that one.

    button.addEventListener(&#39;click&#39;, function(event) =&gt; {
         event.preventDefault();
         // your function here
    });

